Corrupted format abbreviations (`4t\u221a\u2264.`/`8v\u221a\u2264.`) were normalized to `4to.` and `8vo.`. 3. The structural error `<PRICE>` was corrected to `<PRIZE>`. 4. All 17 instances of the stray price separator symbol (`\u221a\u2020`) were removed. 5. Untagged descriptive text ('alle in albho.', 'Ferner, gebunden:') and descriptive contents in `<VOLUME>` ('6. Stuck complet') were wrapped in `<NOTE>` tags to improve structural integrity. 6. Currency subunit corruption (`\u221a\u00fc.`) was replaced with `ss.`. 7. Minor semantic corrections were made ('Tempe Helveticg' to 'Tempe Helvetica', 'Homen' to 'Homer').
